[
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01945\">Beware</st> to the <st data-num=\"04754\" class=\"\">filthy</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01351\" class=\"\">stained</st> city;<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> filled with <st data-num=\"03238\" class=\"\">oppressors</st>!<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">She <st data-num=\"03808 08085 06963\">is disobedient</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">she has <st data-num=\"03808 03947\">refused</st> <st data-num=\"04148\" class=\"\">correction</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">She does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">trust</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>;<p class=\"poetry\">she has <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07126\" class=\"\">sought the advice</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">of</st><n id=\"3\" /> her <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">Her</st> <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">princes</st><n id=\"1\" /> are as fierce as <st data-num=\"07580\" class=\"\">roaring</st> <st data-num=\"0738\" class=\"\">lions</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">her <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">rulers</st><n id=\"3\" /> are as hungry as <st data-num=\"02061\" class=\"\">wolves</st> in the <st data-num=\"06160\" class=\"\">desert</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">who completely <st data-num=\"03808 01633\">devour</st> their prey by <st data-num=\"01242\" class=\"\">morning</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Her <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st> are <st data-num=\"06348\" class=\"\">proud</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">they are <st data-num=\"0900\" class=\"\">deceitful</st> <st data-num=\"0582\" class=\"\">men</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Her <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> have <st data-num=\"02490\" class=\"\">defiled</st> <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">what is holy</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">they have <st data-num=\"02554\" class=\"\">broken</st> God\u2019s <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">laws</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">just</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> resides<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">within</st> her;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">commits</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"05766\" class=\"\">unjust acts</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01242\" class=\"\">Every</st> <st data-num=\"01242\" class=\"\">morning</st> he <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">reveals</st><n id=\"3\" /> his <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">At <st data-num=\"0216\" class=\"\">dawn</st> he appears <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">without</st> <st data-num=\"05737\" class=\"\">fail</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Yet the <st data-num=\"05767\" class=\"\">unjust</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"01322\" class=\"\">shame</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">destroyed</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"06438\" class=\"\">walled cities</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"08074\" class=\"\">are in ruins</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"02717\" class=\"\">turned</st> their <st data-num=\"02351\" class=\"\">streets</st> <st data-num=\"02717\" class=\"\">into ruins</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01097\" class=\"\">no</st> one <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">passes through</st> them.<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> <st data-num=\"06658\" class=\"\">are desolate</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01097 0369\">no</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">lives there</st>.<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">thought</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u2018<st data-num=\"0389\" class=\"\">Certainly</st> you will <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">respect</st><n id=\"2\" /> me!<p class=\"poetry\">Now you will <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">accept</st> <st data-num=\"04148\" class=\"\">correction</st>!\u2019<p class=\"poetry\">If she had done so, her <st data-num=\"04585\" class=\"\">home</st><n id=\"3\" /> would <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> be <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">destroyed</st><n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">by <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">punishments</st> I have <st data-num=\"06485 05921\">threatened</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0403\" class=\"\">But</st> they <st data-num=\"07925\" class=\"\">eagerly</st> <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">sinned</st><p class=\"poetry\">in <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">everything</st> they <st data-num=\"05949\" class=\"\">did</st>.<n id=\"6\" /></p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">Therefore</st> you must <st data-num=\"02442\" class=\"\">wait patiently</st><n id=\"1\" /> for me,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cfor the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> when I <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">attack</st> and take <st data-num=\"05706\" class=\"\">plunder</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">have</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">decided</st><n id=\"3\" /> to <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">gather</st> <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">together</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">assemble</st> <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdoms</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">so I can <st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">pour out</st> my <st data-num=\"02195\" class=\"\">fury</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> them\u2014<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> my <st data-num=\"02740\" class=\"\">raging</st> <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st><n id=\"4\" /> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st> will be <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">consumed</st><p class=\"poetry\">by my <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fiery</st> <st data-num=\"07068\" class=\"\">anger</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Know for sure that</st> I will <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">then</st> <st data-num=\"02015 0413\">enable</st><p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">nations</st> to give me <st data-num=\"01305\" class=\"\">acceptable</st> <st data-num=\"08193\" class=\"\">praise</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> of them will <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">invoke</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st> when they pray<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and will <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">worship</st> him <st data-num=\"07926 0259\">in unison</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">From <st data-num=\"05676\" class=\"\">beyond</st> the <st data-num=\"05104\" class=\"\">rivers</st> of <st data-num=\"03568\" class=\"\">Ethiopia</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">those who <st data-num=\"06282\" class=\"\">pray</st> to me, my <st data-num=\"06327\" class=\"\">dispersed people,</st><n id=\"2\" /><p class=\"poetry\">will <st data-num=\"02986\" class=\"\">bring</st> me <st data-num=\"04503\" class=\"\">tribute</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">In <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> you<n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">be ashamed</st> of <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> your <st data-num=\"05949 0834 06586\">rebelliousness</st> against me,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">then</st> I will <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">remove</st> from your <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">midst</st> those who <st data-num=\"01346\" class=\"\">proudly</st> <st data-num=\"05947\" class=\"\">boast</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and you will <st data-num=\"03808 05750\">never</st> <st data-num=\"03254\" class=\"\">again</st> <st data-num=\"01361\" class=\"\">be arrogant</st> on my <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">holy</st> <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">hill</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07604\" class=\"\">leave</st> in your <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">midst</st> a <st data-num=\"06041\" class=\"\">humble</st> and <st data-num=\"01800\" class=\"\">meek</st> group of <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and they will <st data-num=\"02620\" class=\"\">find safety</st> in the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">presence</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelites</st> who <st data-num=\"07611\" class=\"\">remain</st><n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">act</st> <st data-num=\"05766\" class=\"\">deceitfully</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01696 03577\">lie</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and a <st data-num=\"08649\" class=\"\">deceitful</st> <st data-num=\"03956\" class=\"\">tongue</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> be <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">found</st> in their <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouths</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">they</st> will <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">graze</st> peacefully like sheep<n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"07257\" class=\"\">lie down</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> one will <st data-num=\"02729\" class=\"\">terrify</st> them.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07442\" class=\"\">Shout for joy</st>, <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07321\" class=\"\">Shout out</st>, <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08055\" class=\"\">Be happy</st> and <st data-num=\"05937\" class=\"\">boast</st> with <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> your <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st>, <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">removed</st> the <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">judgment</st> against you;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he has <st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">turned back</st> your <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, is in your <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">midst</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">longer</st> need to <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">fear</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">disaster</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">On <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> they will <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">Don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">be afraid</st>, <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hands</st> must <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> be <st data-num=\"07503\" class=\"\">paralyzed</st> from panic!<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> is in your <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">midst</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he is a <st data-num=\"01368\" class=\"\">warrior</st> who can <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">deliver</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"07797\" class=\"\">takes</st> <st data-num=\"08057\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"07797\" class=\"\">delight</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st> you;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"02318\" class=\"\">renews</st> you by his <st data-num=\"0160\" class=\"\">love</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"07440\" class=\"\">shouts</st> for <st data-num=\"01523\" class=\"\">joy</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> you.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cAs for those who <st data-num=\"03013\" class=\"\">grieve</st> because they cannot attend the <st data-num=\"04150\" class=\"\">festivals</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">took</st> them <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">away</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> you;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">became</st> <st data-num=\"04864\" class=\"\">tribute</st> and were a <st data-num=\"02781\" class=\"\">source of shame</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> you.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, at <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> I will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">deal with</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">those</st> who <st data-num=\"06031\" class=\"\">mistreated</st> you.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">rescue</st> the <st data-num=\"06760\" class=\"\">lame</st> sheep<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">gather together</st> the <st data-num=\"05080\" class=\"\">scattered</st> sheep.<p class=\"poetry\">I will take away their <st data-num=\"01322\" class=\"\">humiliation</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">make</st> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st> <st data-num=\"08416\" class=\"\">admire</st> and <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">respect</st> them.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Zephaniah",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">At <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> I will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">lead</st> <st data-num=\"07622\" class=\"\">you</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">at the <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> I <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">gather</st> you <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">together</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Be sure of this</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> I will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">make</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">nations</st> of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st> <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">respect</st> and <st data-num=\"08416\" class=\"\">admire</st> you<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">when you <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">see</st> me <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">restore</st> <st data-num=\"07622\" class=\"\">you</st>,\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  }
]